<HL>
   Forest-Products
   Firms Post Losses
   For First Quarter
   ----
   By Chip Johnson
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/17/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C13
</SO>
<CO>
   BCC LPX TJCO
</CO>
